-- Portsmouth Soccer Club May Be Bought by Italian, Times Reports
-- B y   M i c h a e l   P a t t e r s o n
-- 2012-01-15T11:41:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-15/portsmouth-soccer-club-may-be-bought-by-italian-times-reports.html
Italian businessman Joseph Cala is
the leader in talks to buy English  soccer club  Portsmouth, the
Sunday Times reported, citing people close to the discussions.  Cala once owned a soccer team in  Italy  for less than two
weeks, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
